{"tid":355461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【興德之亂】教局證實收到校長律師信！傳對方拒赴聆訊","createTime":"2017-08-11T10:07:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T09:33:40.000Z","uid":24160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28ee509d2bad04212d8fa74ce79e0a917c62b9c9","tid":355461,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:07:03.000Z","msg":"【更新實況】<br />\n屯門興德學校問題愈揭愈多，被指管理不善，又強迫教師到深圳派傳單、准許部分全年缺席的「影子學生」升班，涉嫌詐騙津貼。教育局早前委派數人到校出任校董，協助處理管理問題，昨日屯門重案組派員到學校搜證；校長陳章萍昨日以病假為由未有出現。教育局周五證實，已收到代表校長陳章萍的律師發出的信函，並正在處理。<br />\n<br />\n另外教育局要求陳章萍在下星期一和教育局會面或作出書面陳述，有消息引述興德學校校監鍾佳榮透露，<span style=\"color: red;\">陳章萍不會出席教育局聆訊，將會由律師代表書面回覆。</span><br />\n<br />\n日前教育局曾表示，自2月起不時接獲與興德有關的行政和管理不善投訴，部份個案已完成調查，當中發現多項違規問題，包括學校曾批准多名註冊後未有正式入讀的學生長時間保留學位；未有按規定在學生連續缺課第7日時向教育局呈報；未有遵守《教育規例》及《資助則例》處理教師解僱事宜等，當局仍在深入審核興德的財務狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170811&amp;guid=57066783&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170811%26guid%3D57066783%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=vJ%2Fr8w8JOc3Zr1%2BfMQSHpL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=68c32715\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170811%26guid%3D57066783%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=0a4459c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170811&amp;guid=57066783&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n記得交餅卡呀 校長😭😭😭<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.tenor.co/images/89034319877ff5a21273ff41a17b140d/tenor.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.tenor.co%2Fimages%2F89034319877ff5a21273ff41a17b140d%2Ftenor.gif&h=dc9abe78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n⌃陳校長示意圖"},{"pid":"096b4121f255d914d1524eedd59919e4d3e2c2aa","tid":355461,"uid":111425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:08:52.000Z","msg":"點解犯法都可以咁撚串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要黃晒全港都知 政府一定唔會比面全力鋤鳩個肥婆wow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4d2dfbf7cd9c479e0bdfcc2d91fe9fadd7b51c","tid":355461,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T01:18:24.000Z","msg":"偽造文書wo, 夠晒料刑事檢控啦，仲等咩？"},{"pid":"601bba367464fa17e950e06e8bbb1d19787a23b4","tid":355461,"uid":64582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T01:22:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>偽造文書wo, 夠晒料刑事檢控啦，仲等咩？</blockquote><br />\n肥婆咁老定，好似好大勢力咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f71b48ba55157973fbcc60d8072a4ad67ebf96d","tid":355461,"uid":115525,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T01:24:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解犯法都可以咁撚串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要黃晒全港都知 政府一定唔會比面全力鋤鳩個肥婆wow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥讚揚蔡若蓮的履歷非常合適出任副局長。<br />\n教育局副局長蔡若蓮：興德影子學生「不需跟進」<br />\n<br />\n蔡若蓮在專欄中承認，局方在確定實際在學人數方面仍有改進空間，指會研究改善現行點算學生人數的方法，以令收集的資料更準確，但指個別學校的不當做法，不應破壞教育局與學校的互信，「教育局亦不應因此全面核查所有學校呈報的學生資料，以免對學校造成不必要的滋擾」。<br />\n<br />\n加埋鄉事派校董 真係鋤到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d43043a4339bc22ec5c23aa28e99cbddff2cf2e5","tid":355461,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T01:26:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解犯法都可以咁撚串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要黃晒全港都知 政府一定唔會比面全力鋤鳩個肥婆wow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥讚揚蔡若蓮的履歷非常合適出任副